%N A029231 Expansion of 1/((1-x^2)*(1-x^7)*(1-x^9)*(1-x^11)).
%C A029231 Number of partitions of n into parts 2, 7, 9, and 11. - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jun 02 2014
%H A029231 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A029231/b029231.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
